#| "to the south, and the <ref>dst='great_ocean' text='ocean'</ref> to the "
#| "west. More information is found in the historical narrative of Wesnoth.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "    • Notable cities:\n"
#| "          ◦ Elensefar: The capital, located on an island in the "
